It is a widespread species distributed from Mexico to Peru . The species has been reported for Acapulco, Mexico ; Corinto, Nicaragua; Ecuador (
Kuekenthal 1924
), from Santa Clara Island to Esmeraldas (
Rivera and Martinez 2011
) and Panama . We have observed it at several sites along the Pacific coast from Mexico to Peru . The depth range is from 3 to 25 m, but mostly it occurs at 8 to 15 m.
